“Every day is a fight. Every day I’m trying to get better.”
 
With summer break on the horizon, members of The Academy have one final chance to leave a lasting impression with a pivotal match against the Philadelphia Union. 
 
[From B/R Football x @audi] #GoalsDriveProgress
